snippet.title: The Battle Cats POP! - Trailer
snippet.description:
Rampage across the globe with weird 'n wild Cats in an exciting but straight-forward tower defense adventure! Collect 100s of fightin' Cats to power up your army, take down bizarre and hilarious enemies and win glorious treasure!

The official Nintendo site: http://www.nintendo.com/
